  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Chalet Hotel Breithorn is a lovely hotel full of charm and with over 100 years of history. It has been tastefully restored whilst keeping all its traditional Alpine features.</p>
<p>There is a spacious lounge/bar and reception area with beautiful carved vaulted wooden ceilings. The restaurant is on the lower ground floor and where all meals are taken including our 5 course dinners, all served with quality wines. There is also a sun terrace and wellness centre with sauna, steam room, whirlpool and massage showers. There are a total of 31 bedrooms all stylishly designed with attractive wooden features, with twin or double beds and en suite facilities. Most of the large and superior rooms have an extra bed for a child. On the 4th floor are larger superior rooms which have mountain views and either shower or hydromassage bath. The junior suite on the 4th floor has a lounge and separate bedroom. With the centre of Champoluc and the main gondola just a 5 minute walk away, the Chalet Hotel Breithorn provides an ideal base for a walking holiday.</p>]]></description>
